asympvar                Asymptotic Variance
b50, p50 and b64        Simulated Data sets which Illustrate the Usage
                        of the Package geoRglm
binom.krige             Conditional Simulation and Prediction for the
                        Binomial-logit Spatial model
binom.krige.bayes       Bayesian Posterior Simulation and Prediction
                        for the Binomial Spatial model
covariog                Empirical Covariogram for a Model with
                        log-link and an Underlying Gaussian Field
covariog.model.env      Envelope for Empirical Covariogram for the
                        Poisson-log normal model
geoRglm-defunct         Defunct Functions in the Package geoRglm
hist.glm.krige.bayes    Plots Sample from Posterior Distributions
image.glm.krige.bayes   Plots Results of the Predictive Distribution
lines.covariomodel      Line with a Covariogram Model
mcmc.control            Defines options for the MCMC-algorithm
model.glm.control       Defines model options
output.glm.control      Defines output options
plot.covariogram        Plot Empirical Covariogram
pois.krige              Conditional Simulation and Prediction for the
                        Poisson Spatial model with a link function
                        from the Box-Cox class
pois.krige.bayes        Bayesian Posterior Simulation and Prediction
                        for the Poisson Spatial model
prior.glm.control       Defines prior options
rongelap                Radionuclide Concentrations on Rongelap Island
